Description:
Among the trees of the swamp, you find an old lady resting in front of her hut. She tells you she thought no one would find her here, but it seems she can’t escape her fame. 

When you explain that you’re just passing through, she sighs with relief. She reveals that she was once the best gladiatrix in the Velkarath arena and came here seeking peace with her retinue. 

However, if you prove yourselves skillful fighters, she may give you an arena badge to challenge Velkarath coliseum’s special trial.
DescriptionAction: Do you want the arena badge that she is offering?
